short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Manage YouTube creators, save timestamps, and take notes

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: You can now save content creators timestamps, take notes about the video, and get most viewed video data from any YouTube channel. Data can be exported to a file so you can see what titles are getting the most views.
